social_posts.post_text: We are open! Our website is almost ready but we are taking bookings via email currently. Hop to it as we have snow and we are filling up! hello@nobleandproper.com

13 years ago this young buck and I tied the knot. 13 years! How?!? People ask me all the time how we do it and run businesses together. Folks, it’s not always easy, but let me put it this way, I married my best friend and my biggest fan. It’s a blessing that I get to spend as much time as I do with him. Not a day goes by that he doesn’t have me doubled over in laughter, he’s beyond thoughtful, he does anything and everything to always make sure that I am happy and feel supported, he pushes me to always set my goals and go after them, he is still my number one fan and will forever be my best friend. He’s also pretty damn hot, so there’s that to 😉 Sven, you are a true dreamboat. Life is just simply the best by your side. I said it once and I’ll say it again, do yourself a favor and marry your best friend. Für immer ❤️ Prost to 14!

Going to be doing a little giveaway to come stay with us @nobleandproper later this week. Make sure to be following my stories and posts so you don’t miss out! The snow is falling once again and the slopes are calling your name! ❄️ 🎿

My @nobleandproper giveaway contest will start on Monday! Tell all yo friends! Set a reminder. You don’t want to miss the chance for a FREE stay with us!

It’s time to announce the contest winner! Or should I say winners? Yep, it’s my birthday week so instead of 1 winner, I’m making it 3 💁🏼‍♀️Congrats @bludauart @samanthamausner @bailey_kaufmann ! You 3 are the winners of a 1 night stay @nobleandproper. Shoot me a DM for details on your adventure that awaits ☺️ But wait, there’s more! Because I’m feeling great, and in honor of my birthday on the 25th, I’m offering everyone that participated in the contest 25% off of a stay @nobleandproper through the month of March! Shoot me a DM to receive your code and details. This only applies to people that entered the contest and met the entry requirements. Thanks for entering and stay tuned for more fun giveaways!
Take a walk on the wild side. Elfriede’s Haus @nobleandproper with the cutest Kermit & Miss Piggy bath. Making all your selfie dreams come true. 📸: @jenny_siegwart

Welcome to 4 Nord. I got to have some fun selecting the furnishings, paint and wallpaper for our hip as shit rental on Moonlight Beach in Encinitas. Sexy, moody and a total vibe. This is just a little sneak peek. If you are interested in renting this baby, shoot me a DM.

Bringing you some 4 Nord style. Reupholstered chairs and wallpaper. What dreams are made of. Our doors are open to have you come stay with us.

Can you kick it? Yes you can! Welcome to @unioncowork in the Arts District in LA. I got to design this whole space a few years back and it’s still a favorite of mine. I wonder why 😉🌈 I had so much fun collaborating with kick ass local artists and vendors to bring this colorful place to life. It’s my go to place when working in LA. If you are needing a spot to post up when in LA or looking for office space to rent, check them out!
Lay me down 💤

social_posts.post_text: 4/4/09 this man asked me to marry him and we began a new chapter in our lives. On 4/4/23 we are boarding a one way flight to NYC with cats in tow to embark on a whole new chapter and adventure. An adventure we have been talking about for the last 10 years! It’s been a whirlwind of emotions and lots of work to get here but we are finally ready to take on NYC full time and create lots of new memories! Shout out to my absolutely amazing husband who has been my biggest rock and support throughout this whole thing. I promise my craziness will come to a halt soon 😜 Let me tell you, if you dream it and you want it, make it happen! It’s never to late and time flies!

We are Noble + Proper. A boutique four season mountain lake escape, where mountain wonderland meets hospitality. A place that was curated with memories of times from the past with a bit of a twist. We invite you to join us for a Noble moment and a Proper Stay.

Spring has sprung and we are offering 25% off of all bookings made from now till 5/31! Use code GETSPRUNG at checkout.
Life lately 🗽
Home sweet home 🏠
Gallery walls 📸
A new take on photos of your children. I’m all about it. Ugly crying is so in!
Weekend plans? We got a seat for you @nobleandproper Shoot an email to hello@nobleandproper.com and mention Handsome Salt and get 20% off to come stay with us. Just because it’s Thursday 🤗

Highly recommend surprise trips to see your family. To say my heart is full, is an understatement. Can’t even watch this video without crying. Multiple. Times. Words of advice, just book the damn trip. Love these 2 to pieces!
Kiss my air.

I like my nails how I like my design, eclectic and wild. If it’s to hot for you, stay out of my kitchen 😜
Patterns, texture, color. It’s what I do. If you’re not having fun, what are you doing? @nobleandproper is my design wonderland ☺️
Pura Vida with a side of tan lines 🇨🇷
Hanging out 🤙

Out here getting whiski.

I can’t get enough of you ❤️

I don’t know if it’s quite possible to love someone more. Since we start celebrating his birthday in German time, the clock has struck and this guy is now 40! Could not be more proud to be your wife and call you my best friend. Sven, you truly are the spice of life. Für Immer ❤️ Happy Birthday Schatz!

And after 12 days of planes, trains, automobiles, and 10 of those days filled with 75+ miles of walking, that’s a wrap on the “This is 40” trip. Thank you to all of you who helped me pull off this epic trip for Sven! You know who you are, cause I texted you non stop 😜 And big shout out to the boys for making the trip! Sven, cheers to 40! Love you für immer!

Have been planning for this smile and moment for months! Was worth every tear to get here to see it through! Anfield Road was everything and more. Embrace the spontaneous moments! England it’s been real but, the Simons are out ✌🏼 And Svenny, you’ll never walk alone 😘
“This is 40” (him, not me). Boys can keep secrets ☺️ Love these brothers of mine and the epic surprise we pulled off in London. They kept asking if I was making a documentary. Why yes, yes I am.

People keep asking what I am working on since I am “slightly” behind on sharing deets. I am knee deep in construction on this bad boy in NYC. Here she is before. You will remember her from the bathroom tile 🤤 Stay tuned. #12onthewest
We shall call this one, heartbreaker. They may have had to physically remove me to demo this bathroom floor. They even asked if I wanted to take the first hammer to it. I could never. #12onthewest
There’s no place I’d rather be. This smile and this moment. YNWA.
If the fit ain’t colorful, I don’t want it. Always surrounded by design inspo.

Happy Birthday to the best dad out there! Currently crushing 74 miles on a bike like it’s no big deal to celebrate. I hear it all the time “no way your dad is that old!”. It’s called #beastmode. He has always been my biggest fan and supporter, my first coach and the reason I am where I am today. He always believed in me, even when I didn’t believe in myself. This is what great dads do. They push you, because they know how great you are. And although as a sassy young kid, we don’t appreciate it then, we grow up and find deep value and gratitude with age. Happy Birthday to the first man that ever loved me. You are truly appreciated and loved! I love you ❤️ @surfdougie

18 years ago we met on this soccer field. Well actually it was in the athletic training room where my first words to you were, “I smell really bad”, as I sniffed my armpit. And it was love at first sniff. But, our true love story began on October 29, 2005 at a Halloween party. Where it’s still debatable who made the first move…Sven. Regardless, best decision I made to make that 3 hour drive to SLO and take a chance. Love our love story. And love you @svensimon24 I want to have it all with you! Happy Dateversary! ❤️
